Package com.jidesoft.converter

Interface Summary
ConverterContextSupport The interface indicates the class who extends it can support ConverterContext.
ObjectConverter An interface that can convert a object to a String and convert from String to object.
 

Class Summary
AbstractContext AbstractContext is a generic context class.
ArrayConverter An abstract class that is extented by any converters that convert to/from an array-like format, such as 1, 2, 3.
BooleanConverter Convertor which converts Boolean to String and converts it back.
CacheMap CacheMap is a two level HashMap.
CalendarConverter Convertor which converts Date to String and converts it back.
ColorConverter Convertor which converts Color to String and converts it back.
ConverterContext The context object used by ObjectConverter.
DateConverter Convertor which converts Date to String and converts it back.
DefaultObjectConverter Default object converters that convert a object to a String using toString().
DimensionConverter Convertor which converts Dimension to String and converts it back.
DoubleConverter Convertor which converts Double to String and converts it back.
FileConverter Convertor which converts File to String and converts it back.
FloatConverter Convertor which converts Float to String and converts it back.
FontNameConverter Convertor which converts Font Name String to String and converts it back.
HexColorConverter Converts Color to/from #xxxxxx format.
IntegerConverter Convertor which converts Integer to String and converts it back.
LongConverter Convertor which converts Long to String and converts it back.
MonthConverter Convertor which converts Date to String and converts it back.
NaturalNumberConverter Convertor which converts Integer to String and converts it back.
NumberConverter Convertor which converts Number to String and converts it back.
ObjectConverterManager A global object that can register converter with a type and a ConverterContext.
PointConverter Convertor which converts Point to String and converts it back.
RectangleConverter Convertor which converts Rectangle to String and converts it back.
RgbColorConverter Converts Color to/from "XXX, XXX, XXX" format.
ShortConverter Convertor which converts Short to String and converts it back.
StringConverter Convertor which converts String to String and converts it back.
